Package hu.elte.txtuml.api.assocends

Contains some interfaces which provide an abstraction to association end properties, like navigability and multiplicity.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Multiplicity
    A base interface to represent the multiplicity property of association ends.
    Multiplicity.One
    Implementing classes of this interface represent association ends in the model which have a multiplicity of 1.
    Multiplicity.OneToUnlimited
    Implementing classes of this interface represent association ends in the model which have a multiplicity of 1..*.
    Multiplicity.ZeroToOne
    Implementing classes of this interface represent association ends in the model which have a multiplicity of 0..1.
    Multiplicity.ZeroToUnlimited
    Implementing classes of this interface represent association ends in the model which have a multiplicity of 0..*.
    Navigability
    A base interface to represent the navigability property of association ends.
    Navigability.Navigable
    Implementing classes of this interface represent navigable association ends in the model.
    Navigability.NonNavigable
    Implementing classes of this interface represent non-navigable association ends in the model.

Package hu.elte.txtuml.api.assocends Description

Contains some interfaces which provide an abstraction to association end properties, like navigability and multiplicity.

See the documentation of Model for an overview on modeling in txtUML.

Author:
Gabor Ferenc Kovacs
